(574, 1, 'TEKKEN 8 (PC) - Steam Key - GLOBAL', 'Tekken 8, the eighth main installment and tenth overall in the series, is an anticipated fighting game for both single-player and multiplayer modes, developed by Bandai Namco Studios and Arika. It marks a significant stride forward in the Tekken series, as the first major fighting title to employ Unreal Engine 5, promising a more immersive and visually stunning gaming experience.', 'Fighting', '2002-10-15', 'Steam', '10.88', NULL, 2, 'img1-TEKKEN8(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img2-TEKKEN8(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img3-TEKKEN8(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'GLOBAL', 'Key'),
(576, 1, 'Suicide Squad: Kill the Justice League (PC) - Steam Key - GLOBAL', 'Suicide Squad: Kill The Justice League is an action video game set in the DC Comics universe, developed by Rocksteady Studios and released thanks to Warner Bros Games in 2022. It is hilarious and dynamic combat gameplay from the creators of the Batman: Arkham series. The end of the superheroes is coming when their actions begin threatening the whole Earth. Only one group can stop the evil Superman and his crew - Suicide Squad.', 'Action', '2019-09-20', 'Steam', '12.23', NULL, 2, 'img1-SuicideSquad:KilltheJusticeLeague(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img2-SuicideSquad:KilltheJusticeLeague(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img3-SuicideSquad:KilltheJusticeLeague(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'GLOBAL', 'Key'),
(577, 1, 'Horizon Forbidden West | Complete Edition (PC) - Steam Key - GLOBAL', 'The game sets the player in an open-world game with a post-apocalyptic western United States all around them. Taking control over a huntress, the player has to survive in a world full of dangerous machines ready to attack at any moment.', 'Games', '2016-02-25', 'Steam', '67.48', NULL, 3, 'img1-HorizonForbiddenWest|CompleteEdition(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img2-HorizonForbiddenWest|CompleteEdition(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img3-HorizonForbiddenWest|CompleteEdition(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'GLOBAL', 'Key'),
(578, 1, 'Project Zomboid (PC) - Steam Gift - GLOBAL', 'The project was first released as a technological demo in 2011. Since then, PZ is being constantly developed and it regularly receives new content and updates improving the gameplay experience. Project Zomboid allows players to experience the life of one of few survivors, lost in a world full of flesh-eating monsters. The game features a vast, open-world map, a complex crafting system, and many mechanics, characteristic for survival games genre.', 'RPG', '2020-10-29', 'Steam', '42.53', NULL, 5, 'img1-ProjectZomboid(PC)-SteamGift-GLOBAL', 'img2-ProjectZomboid(PC)-SteamGift-GLOBAL', 'img3-ProjectZomboid(PC)-SteamGift-GLOBAL', 'GLOBAL', 'Key'),
(581, 1, 'Destiny 2: The Final Shape + Annual Pass (PC) - Steam Key - GLOBAL', 'The Standard edition of The Final Shape includes the new story campaign, three new Supers, a new destination, new weapons and armor to collect, and the first Episode in the year of The Final Shape. ', 'Extra Content', '2017-10-17', 'Steam', '30.05', NULL, 6, 'img1-Destiny2:TheFinalShape+AnnualPass(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img2-Destiny2:TheFinalShape+AnnualPass(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img3-Destiny2:TheFinalShape+AnnualPass(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'GLOBAL', 'Key'),
(582, 1, 'Batman: Arkham Collection (PC) - Steam Key - GLOBAL', 'Batman: Arkham Collection is a bundle of the three main games in the Arkham series, featuring the character of DC’s Dark Knight: Arkham Asylum, Arkham City, and Arkham Knight, as well as the Season Pass for the latter one. All three games feature open-world environments of Arkham Asylum, and later on the entire Gotham City, which the player can explore while carrying out the story missions, side-quests and finding various collectibles. Throughout the series, Batman will face many of his most notable adversaries, including Two-Face, the Penguin, Riddler, and the Joker, his greatest foe. All of the games in the Arkham series have received critical acclaim and are considered to be one of the best titles featuring Gotham’s Dark Knight.', 'Games', '2021-07-14', 'Steam', '43.69', NULL, 2, 'img1-Batman:ArkhamCollection(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img2-Batman:ArkhamCollection(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img3-Batman:ArkhamCollection(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'GLOBAL', 'Key'),
(583, 1, '7 Days to Die Steam Key GLOBAL', 'World War III came and gone, and all that\'s left is you, some wildlife and hordes of zombies. In 7 Days to Die you have to hold your own against increasingly more dangerous hordes of zombies. How long can you survive? It\'s never going to get easy.', 'Action', '2020-10-27', 'Steam', '49.3', NULL, 0, 'img1-7DaystoDieSteamKeyGLOBAL', 'img2-7DaystoDieSteamKeyGLOBAL', 'img3-7DaystoDieSteamKeyGLOBAL', 'GLOBAL', 'Key'),
(584, 1, 'Nightingale (PC) - Steam Key - GLOBAL', 'Nightingale is a first-person, PVE, open-world survival crafting game played solo or cooperatively with friends. Build, craft, fight and explore as you venture through mystical portals into a variety of amazing and fantastical realms.', 'Adventure', '2019-10-22', 'Steam', '60.34', NULL, 3, 'img1-Nightingale(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img2-Nightingale(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img3-Nightingale(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'GLOBAL', 'Key'),
(585, 1, 'Terraria (PC) - Steam Gift - GLOBAL', 'Dig, fight, explore, build! Nothing is impossible in this action-packed adventure game. The world is your canvas and the ground itself is your paint. ', 'RPG', '2021-11-09', 'Steam', '3.47', NULL, 4, 'img1-Terraria(PC)-SteamGift-GLOBAL', 'img2-Terraria(PC)-SteamGift-GLOBAL', 'img3-Terraria(PC)-SteamGift-GLOBAL', 'GLOBAL', 'Key'),
(586, 1, 'TEKKEN 8 | Deluxe Edition (PC) - Steam Key - GLOBAL', 'Tekken 8, the eighth main installment and tenth overall in the series, is an anticipated fighting game for both single-player and multiplayer modes, developed by Bandai Namco Studios and Arika. It marks a significant stride forward in the Tekken series, as the first major fighting title to employ Unreal Engine 5, promising a more immersive and visually stunning gaming experience.', 'Fighting', '2015-08-05', 'Steam', '17.48', NULL, 5, 'img1-TEKKEN8|DeluxeEdition(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img2-TEKKEN8|DeluxeEdition(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img3-TEKKEN8|DeluxeEdition(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'GLOBAL', 'Key'),
(587, 1, 'NBA 2K24 | Kobe Bryant Edition (PC) - Steam Key - GLOBAL', 'Grab your squad and experience the past, present, and future of hoops culture in NBA 2K24. Enjoy loads of pure, unadulterated action and limitless personalized MyPLAYER options in MyCAREER. Collect an impressive array of legends and build your perfect lineup in MyTEAM. Feel more responsive gameplay and polished visuals while playing with your favorite NBA and WNBA teams in PLAY NOW.', 'Sports', '2019-09-01', 'Steam', '45.81', NULL, 2, 'img1-NBA2K24|KobeBryantEdition(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img2-NBA2K24|KobeBryantEdition(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img3-NBA2K24|KobeBryantEdition(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'GLOBAL', 'Key'),
(588, 1, 'Assetto Corsa | Ultimate Edition Steam Key GLOBAL', 'Assetto Corsa was developed by Italian studio Kumos Simulazioni. The developers focused on creating the most realistic racing simulator. In the game, players get access to over 170 officially licensed cars, including innovative prototypes and legendary F1 and GT Series machines. Every car has been carefully designed, with extreme attention to detail, in order to deliver the most realistic experience.', 'Racing', '2019-09-01', 'Steam', '6.13', NULL, 4, 'img1-AssettoCorsa|UltimateEditionSteamKeyGLOBAL', 'img2-AssettoCorsa|UltimateEditionSteamKeyGLOBAL', 'img3-AssettoCorsa|UltimateEditionSteamKeyGLOBAL', 'GLOBAL', 'Key'),
(589, 1, 'Minecraft: Java & Bedrock Edition (PC) - Microsoft Store Key - GLOBAL', 'The ultimate sandbox game returns in its most complete edition! Players won\'t have to choose anymore and can enjoy Minecraft however they want whenever they want! Craft, fight, build and survive in a procedurally generated world! Explore many different biomes and encounter weird and dangerous creatures! Build majestic structures, elaborate contraptions or even entire villages! The possibilities are endless and countless hours of great fun await you!', 'Adventure', '2016-01-26', 'Microsoft Store', '11.91', NULL, 1, 'img1-Minecraft:Java&BedrockEdition(PC)-MicrosoftStoreKey-GLOBAL', 'img2-Minecraft:Java&BedrockEdition(PC)-MicrosoftStoreKey-GLOBAL', 'img3-Minecraft:Java&BedrockEdition(PC)-MicrosoftStoreKey-GLOBAL', 'GLOBAL', 'Key'),
(590, 1, 'Pacific Drive | Deluxe Edition (PC) - Steam Key - GLOBAL', 'Pacific Drive is a first-person driving survival game with your car as your only companion. Navigate a surreal reimagining of the Pacific Northwest, and face supernatural dangers as you venture into the Olympic Exclusion Zone.', 'Action', '2019-01-11', 'Steam', '43.59', NULL, 3, 'img1-PacificDrive|DeluxeEdition(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img2-PacificDrive|DeluxeEdition(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img3-PacificDrive|DeluxeEdition(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'GLOBAL', 'Key'),
(591, 1, 'Deep Rock Galactic (PC) - Steam Key - GLOBAL', 'Deep Rock Galactic is the original first-person shooter developed by the Danish studio Ghost Ship Games. Players take on the role of spaces dwarves working to extract raw materials from the most dangerous caves, where even the bravest daredevils cannot venture.', 'Action', '2015-03-11', 'Steam', '49.29', NULL, 5, 'img1-DeepRockGalactic(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img2-DeepRockGalactic(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img3-DeepRockGalactic(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'GLOBAL', 'Key'),
(592, 1, 'TEKKEN 8 | Ultimate Edition (PC) - Steam Key - GLOBAL', 'Tekken 8, the eighth main installment and tenth overall in the series, is an anticipated fighting game for both single-player and multiplayer modes, developed by Bandai Namco Studios and Arika. It marks a significant stride forward in the Tekken series, as the first major fighting title to employ Unreal Engine 5, promising a more immersive and visually stunning gaming experience.', 'Fighting', '2018-02-22', 'Steam', '51.78', NULL, 5, 'img1-TEKKEN8|UltimateEdition(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img2-TEKKEN8|UltimateEdition(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img3-TEKKEN8|UltimateEdition(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'GLOBAL', 'Key'),
(593, 1, 'Monster Hunter World (PC) - Steam Key - GLOBAL', 'Take a long journey to the New World, following in the footsteps of the Elder Dragons. Can you discover what prompts them to migrate there every decade in the event known as the Elder Crossing? Join the Fifth Fleet and find out!', 'Action', '2011-04-18', 'Steam', '68.44', NULL, 2, 'img1-MonsterHunterWorld(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img2-MonsterHunterWorld(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img3-MonsterHunterWorld(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'GLOBAL', 'Key'),
(594, 1, 'Banishers: Ghosts of New Eden (PC) - Steam Key - GLOBAL', 'New Eden, 1695. Antea Duarte and Red mac Raith are lovers and Banishers, ghost-hunters who vowed to protect the living from the threat of lingering ghosts and specters. Following a disastrous last mission, Antea is fatally wounded, becoming one of the spirits she loathes. In the haunted wilds of North America, the couple desperately searches for a way to liberate Antea from her new plight.', 'RPG', '2019-11-15', 'Steam', '29.66', NULL, 6, 'img1-Banishers:GhostsofNewEden(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img2-Banishers:GhostsofNewEden(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img3-Banishers:GhostsofNewEden(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'GLOBAL', 'Key'),
(596, 1, 'Like a Dragon: Infinite Wealth (PC) - Steam Key - GLOBAL', 'Two larger-than-life heroes, Ichiban Kasuga and Kazuma Kiryu are brought together by the hand of fate, or perhaps something more sinister… Live it up in Japan and explore all that Hawaii has to offer in an RPG adventure so big it spans the Pacific.', 'Adventure', '2022-08-04', 'Steam', '2.15', NULL, 5, 'img1-LikeaDragon:InfiniteWealth(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img2-LikeaDragon:InfiniteWealth(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img3-LikeaDragon:InfiniteWealth(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'GLOBAL', 'Key'),
