(824, 1, 'Fallout 76 | The Pitt Deluxe (PC) - Steam Key - GLOBAL', 'Fallout 76 is a prequel to other games in the Fallout series, developed by Bethesda Softworks. It will be the first online multiplayer title in Bethesda Game Studios? offer. Even though the game is the ninth one in the franchise, its storyline takes place well before the events of even the first Fallout game, just after the first vaults started opening.', 'Games', '2010-09-08', 'Steam', '17.57', NULL, 5, 'img1-Fallout76|ThePittDeluxe(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img2-Fallout76|ThePittDeluxe(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img3-Fallout76|ThePittDeluxe(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'GLOBAL', 'Key'),
