(851, 1, 'Just Cause 3 (PC) - Steam Key - GLOBAL', 'Just Cause 3 is a 2015 action-adventure multiplatform game, developed by Avalanche Studios and published by Square Enix for PC, PlayStation 4 and Xbox One. The game is set on Medici, a fictional Mediterranean island and nation governed by a dictator General Di Ravello. Rico Rodriguez, the protagonist of the previous installment, Just Cause 2 is returning as the main character of the game.  The players are given free choice in exploring the island between missions.', 'Games', '2023-09-18', 'Steam', '5.07', NULL, 5, 'img1-JustCause3(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img2-JustCause3(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img3-JustCause3(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'GLOBAL', 'Key'),
