(1062, 1, 'SPACECOM Steam Key GLOBAL', 'SPACECOM ? a strategic-to-the-bone, starfleet command game with a heavy focus on multiplayer. Spacecom is a battle of strategists in which deception, smart movement, and choices to battle decide victory or defeat. \r\n\r\nNo coincidence, no luck. Spacecom pushes your ability to strategize with a focus on real-time tactics and planning. Use proven maneuvers learned from military legends or devise your own plans. Dominate your enemies in planetary systems with up to six players per campaign. Most of all, you\'ll need a bright mind, cunning, and sound tactics. \r\n\r\nWhen the war begins, leave the little things behind and dive into austere soundscapes as you immerse yourself in starfleet command. From now on, what matters is your grasp of tactics and strategy, not how fast you can click. Spacecom is about creativity in planning, not complexity of game mechanics.', 'Strategy', '2017-09-15', 'Steam', '0.78', NULL, 3, 'img1-SPACECOMSteamKeyGLOBAL', 'img2-SPACECOMSteamKeyGLOBAL', 'img3-SPACECOMSteamKeyGLOBAL', 'GLOBAL', 'Key'),
(1063, 1, 'ConflictCraft Steam Key GLOBAL', '\"ConflictCraft? is a simple strategy game set in an alternate reality where you control the battle against the armies of ISIS. Your goals are to control all points on the map, destroy all enemy bases, and defend your units and strategic resources.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nYour bases generate unit points every 10 seconds, and you can send half of the units from your bases to any position on the map.\r\n\r\n\r\nTo destroy your enemies, you have tanks, attack helicopters, support helicopters, jets, and rocket missiles. Forces can be upgraded, allowing for customized strategies and tactics.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nThere\'s local multiplayer mode with full controller support, play with your friends and compete against each other.\r\n\r\nYou can even create new maps with the built in level editor and challenge the community!', 'Casual', '2012-10-18', 'Steam', '0.2', NULL, 4, 'img1-ConflictCraftSteamKeyGLOBAL', 'img2-ConflictCraftSteamKeyGLOBAL', 'img3-ConflictCraftSteamKeyGLOBAL', 'GLOBAL', 'Key'),
