(1070, 1, 'World War Z (PC) - Steam Key - GLOBAL', 'World War Z is a third-person perspective action game developed by Saber Interactive and published by Focus Home Interactive. The game is an adaptation of World War Z, a 2013 film starring Brad Pitt, based on the novel of the same title by Max Brooks. In World War Z players take control of one of the lucky survivors of the global outbreak which turns infected humans into aggressive, flesh-eating zombies. The game is set in various parts of the globe and tells the stories of survivors trying to hold their ground against the swarm of the undead. The game heavily emphasizes cooperation tactics and features 4 player co-op mode.', 'Games', '2023-04-05', 'Steam', '15.59', NULL, 3, 'img1-WorldWarZ(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img2-WorldWarZ(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'img3-WorldWarZ(PC)-SteamKey-GLOBAL', 'GLOBAL', 'Key'),
