(1279, 1, 'Baldur\'s Gate 3 (Xbox Series X/S) - Xbox Live Key - EUROPE', 'Baldur\'s Gate III is the third installment of the world-famous RPG series set in the Forgotten Realms, developed by Larian Studios for Windows systems. The series was originally started in 1998 by BioWare and it became one of the most known and respected RPG games in the history of gaming. Baldur\'s Gate 3 release date is planned on 2021, however, the game will be available within Early Access starting 30 September 2020.', 'RPG', '2019-02-22', 'Xbox Live', '57.39', NULL, 4, 'img1-Baldur\'sGate3(XboxSeriesX/S)-XboxLiveKey-EUROPE', 'img2-Baldur\'sGate3(XboxSeriesX/S)-XboxLiveKey-EUROPE', 'img3-Baldur\'sGate3(XboxSeriesX/S)-XboxLiveKey-EUROPE', 'EUROPE', 'Key'),
